######################################## Code And Tools ###########################################
## Code
https://github.com/Shopify/polaris - Shopify’s product component library 
https://github.com/airbnb/react-sketchapp - render React components to Sketch
https://github.com/icons8/titanic - A set of animated icons + code to insert them into the webpages
https://github.com/icons8/line-awesome - Replace Font Awesome with modern line icons
https://github.com/skullface/design-resources - Select websites, tools, assets, and readings for working in and learning about design



## Tools
https://polaris.shopify.com/ - Shopify’s product component library
https://launchpad.animaapp.com/ - allows you to publish responsive websites directly from Sketch
https://atlassian.design -  Atlassian's end-to-end design language
https://ludus.one/ -  Slide design and sharing (free tier available)
http://www.purple.pm/ - Collaborative boards that simplify UX planning
http://bradfrost.github.io/style-guide-guide/ - A boilerplate for creating superb style guides
http://ambiance.somethingjustlikethis.com/ - Color palletes to share
https://www.producthunt.com/posts/interactive-nps-benchmarks-delighted - Enter your score, pick the industry & compare your NPS
https://methods.18f.gov/ - A collection of tools to bring human-centered design into your project.
http://www.ego-icons.com - Free Icon sets
https://wake.com/free - A free design collaboration and feedback tool for teams
https://icons8.com/c/animated-icons - 60 free animated icons 
http://facebook.design/soundkit - A collection of interaction sounds for prototypes.
http://designresources.party/ - Select websites, tools assets, and readings for working in and learning about design.

